title: Rampal - Vivaldi Concerti
description:
Here is Jean-Pierre RAMPAL (flute) playing Vivaldi&#039;s concertos for Flute and Orchestra with Il Solisti Veneti (conductor : Claudio Simone) :

no 1 Op 10 "La tempesta di Mare" RV 433 - F dur
no 2 op 10 "La Notte" RV 439 - G moll
no 3 op 10 "Il Cardellino" RV 428 - D dur
no 4 op 10 RV 435 - G dur
no 5 op 10 RV 434 - F dur
no 6 op 10 RV 437 - G dur
RV 427 - D dur
RV 414 - G dur

All tracks are mp3s, 320 kbps, as usual...

Enjoy this !


NB : I have another recording of these concertos by Rampal, but with Ristenpart (it also includes BWV 1067 (orchestral suite in H moll - Bach) ).I do prefer the present version, but if anyone is interested, just leave a comment.
